OL,3,CWimbledon to replace line judges with
OL,4,Celectronic system from next year
OL,6,FA fully automated version of the 'Hawk-
OL,7,FEye' system is to be used at the
OL,8,FWimbledon Championships, ITV News'
OL,9,FAisha Zahid explains
OL,11,FWimbledon will dispense with line
OL,12,Fjudges next year in favour of Live
OL,13,FElectronic Line Calling.
OL,15,FThe technology is already widely used
OL,16,Fin the sport, including at the
OL,17,FAustralian Open and US Open, and the
OL,18,FAll England Club has now made the
OL,19,Fdecision to follow suit.
