OL,3,CWimbledon to replace line judges with
OL,4,Celectronic system from next year
OL,6,FSince 2007, Hawk-Eye has assisted the
OL,7,Fofficials at Wimbledon on certain
OL,8,Fcourts, with players able to challenge
OL,9,Fline calls, but the system will now be
OL,10,Ffully automated across the site,
OL,11,Fincluding during qualifying at
OL,12,FRoehampton.
OL,14,FChief executive Sally Bolton said:
OL,15,F"The decision to introduce Live
OL,16,FElectronic Line Calling at The
OL,17,FChampionships was made following a
OL,18,Fsignificant period of consideration
OL,19,Fand consultation.
