OL,4,Celectronic system from next year
OL,6,F"Having reviewed the results of the
OL,7,Ftesting undertaken at The
OL,8,FChampionships this year, we consider
OL,9,Fthe technology to be sufficiently
OL,10,Frobust and the time is right to take
OL,11,Fthis important step in seeking maximum
OL,12,Faccuracy in our officiating.
OL,14,F"For the players, it will offer them
OL,15,Fthe same conditions they have played
OL,16,Funder at a number of other events on
OL,17,Ftour.
