OL,3,CWimbledon to replace line judges with
OL,4,Celectronic system from next year
OL,6,F"We take our responsibility to balance
OL,7,Ftradition and innovation at Wimbledon
OL,8,Fvery seriously. Line umpires have
OL,9,Fplayed a central role in our
OL,10,Fofficiating set-up at The
OL,11,FChampionships for many decades and we
OL,12,Frecognise their valuable contribution
OL,13,Fand thank them for their commitment
OL,14,Fand service."
OL,16,FThe French Open, which has relied
OL,17,Fsolely on human officials, is now the
OL,18,Foutlier, although it may well follow
OL,19,Fsuit, with all ATP Tour events to
OL,20,Ffeature the technology from next year.
