OL,3,CWimbledon to replace line judges with
OL,4,Celectronic system from next year
OL,6,FOne major concern for Wimbledon had
OL,7,Fbeen the loss of a prestigious
OL,8,Fopportunity for officials and the
OL,9,Feffect this could have at the lower
OL,10,Flevels of the sport, but ultimately
OL,11,Fprogress has won out.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a change to the schedule
OL,14,Fnext year will see the two singles
OL,15,Ffinals pushed back from 2pm on the
OL,16,Ffinal Saturday and Sunday to 4pm, with
OL,17,Fthe men's and women's doubles finals
OL,18,Fto be held first at 1pm.
